  "prompt": "What do if I forget my user id and password of forex card HDFC?",
  "response": "If you forget your user ID and password for your HDFC Forex Card, here are some steps you can take:\n\n1. Online Recovery Options:\n\u2022 Visit the official HDFC Bank website\n\u2022 Click on \"Forgot User ID\" or \"Forgot Password\"\n\u2022 Follow the online recovery process\n\u2022 Provide necessary identification details\n\n2. Contact HDFC Bank Customer Care:\n\u2022 Call HDFC Bank's customer support number\n\u2022 Helpline: 1800-270-3434 or 022-66412121\n\u2022 Verify your identity through KYC documents\n\u2022 Request assistance in resetting credentials\n\n3. Visit Nearest HDFC Bank Branch:\n\u2022 Carry valid ID proof\n\u2022 Request card-related credential reset\n\u2022 Bank executive will help you reset details\n\n4. Mobile Banking App:\n\u2022 Use \"Forgot Password\" option\n\u2022 Verify through registered mobile number\n\u2022 Reset credentials through OTP\n\n5. Email Support:\n\u2022 Write to HDFC Bank's customer support email\n\u2022 Provide necessary identification details\n\u2022 Request credential recovery assistance\n\nRemember to keep your identification documents handy during the recovery process.\n\nTip: Always store login credentials securely to avoid future inconvenience.",
